ReVolt ROM is a custom ROM based on AOKP Sources with cherry-picks from CyanogenMod and ParanoidAndroid. ReVolt ROM offers stability and buttery smooth experience for users. ReVolt ROM is fully open-sourced on GitHub and is fully buildable for all devices.


Team ReVolt Members:
Johnhany97 / Lead Developer , Maintainer
TPoint75 / Co-Developer , User support for HTC One
